{"tid":1295551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"企前排開傘有乜用","createTime":"2019-07-08T05:11:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T05:39:19.000Z","uid":251086,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6c02f246a2d7407cfedb2d712e3c4f6828e80a68","tid":1295551,"uid":251086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:11:14.000Z","msg":"純討論，非分化<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n可以擋住噴霧<br />\n阻擋警視線，保護示威者<br />\n<br />\n壞處：<br />\n阻擋示威者視線，睇唔倒警方推進<br />\n移動速速降低<br />\n<br />\n而開傘能否防禦警攻擊成疑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個人認為，示威者視線重要過避警視線，如果唔係想衝，理論上唔需要硬食噴霧，因可退，所以諗清楚想點先，唔好再亂擺傘陣"},{"pid":"a3fea5b57a9effda60a67745fbd6667c7daba710","tid":1295551,"uid":157470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:12:49.000Z","msg":"遮cam"},{"pid":"e9b600385fa10c0ffa060a183ef5baaa0af94a99","tid":1295551,"uid":228143,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:13:50.000Z","msg":"擺咩都冇用  而家轉左主動拘捕<br />\n<br />\n下下重棍   唔同以前 比時間你對峙再驅散<br />\n<br />\n4面一齊推  你拎ak都打到你冇子彈呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fadb30737c7757733887df685e32800604a5a10d","tid":1295551,"uid":251086,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:14:59.000Z","msg":"仲有，開傘個姿態比人感覺係想衝/守某地方（新聞角度似暴力），如果傘冇實際用途，建議不如少用"},{"pid":"df1b75065f12d0ffd16e33fe379c8a58da39b149","tid":1295551,"uid":124859,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:16:09.000Z","msg":"係無用<br />\n一扯就爛<br />\n下次至少要制盾"},{"pid":"2e2d185d5e3a2722aa66c1417fb9238ae6df9986","tid":1295551,"uid":218215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:18:00.000Z","msg":"遮cam用"},{"pid":"a549ca92ce023c20ff2eff15eb42653dde879769","tid":1295551,"uid":251086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3fea5b57a9effda